{"tid":1002910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上機前 FBI 出手拉人！中國員工又偷 Apple 機密","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T10:36:36.000Z","uid":98777,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20915b13952bcf3315162047bfea5e1f01ab4184","tid":1002910,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"繼去年年中一名 Apple 員工因為從自動駕駛研發中心，盜竊機密電路板、電腦伺服器和下載技術手冊到妻子的電腦被捕後，日前又爆出另一單類似的案件。美國 NBC 報導指 FBI 指控一名在 Apple 工作的中國籍工程師 Jizhong Chen，嘗試偷取 Apple 自動駕駛項目的商業機密資料。<br />\n<br />\n上機前 FBI 出手拉人！中國員工又偷 Apple 機密<br />\n<br />\n報導指有員工向 Apple 舉報，表示這名中國工程師在敏感的工作區域拍照，於是展開調查。Apple 的全球保安部門職員搜尋該工程師的私人電腦，發現內有過千個載有 Apple 知識產權的檔案文件，包括手冊、佈局圖和圖表等，另外還找到過百張在 Apple 大樓內拍攝的照片。其中一張由 Apple 交予 FBI，在 Chen 姓工程師電腦找到的照片，清楚顯示 Apple 設計的自動駕駛汽車線束繪圖。<br />\n<br />\nApple 發現這名工程師除了偷竊公司的機密資料，甚至還向 Apple 的競爭對手，一間中國的自動駕駛汽車公司求職。在這名工程師準備飛往大陸前一天，FBI 出手將之拘捕。這已經是半年內第二宗，涉及中國工程師盜竊 Apple 自動駕駛項目機密的案件，去年 7 月被拘捕的 Xiaolang Zhang 被指偷取機密資料並嘗試交予大陸公司 XMotors。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：nbcbayarea<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/26204/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fnb%2Ftalk%2F1141%2F26204%2F1%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6pq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=81639a89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/nb/talk/1141/26204/1/</a>"},{"pid":"357570049fc76b0c9aa0f049958a50cae6bb1ff2","tid":1002910,"uid":86,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"點解咁on9 <br />\n唔用速遞？"},{"pid":"42913ac513869fd87535a21840f9fbe95545b855","tid":1002910,"uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"357570049fc76b0c9aa0f049958a50cae6bb1ff2","tid":1002910,"uid":86,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"點解咁on9 <br />\n唔用速遞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲請支那賤種做員工仲戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明知支那人一定係間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d7ebfb34a3a411c70c56e79f1a63fca84b292c","tid":1002910,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357570049fc76b0c9aa0f049958a50cae6bb1ff2","tid":1002910,"uid":86,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"點解咁on9 <br />\n唔用速遞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:49:27.000Z","msg":"下次就會喇<br />\n<br />\n不過會再請中國籍員工先算喇"},{"pid":"b84249d7606fd52cece93d72284d59bd220690b3","tid":1002910,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4988ae4d8bc44a65dc1414a149880cadb3f463f7","tid":1002910,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1525ebb07432a33ebecfb1cefc2dbb1b297054","tid":1002910,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想走去邊?"},{"pid":"adea3bf2922e35f386b8b8c44c5934e2a5f3885b","tid":1002910,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">Apple 的全球保安部門職員搜尋該工程師的私人電腦，發現內有過千個載有 Apple 知識產權的檔案文件，包括手冊、佈局圖和圖表等，另外還找到過百張在 Apple 大樓內拍攝的照片。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n用咩方法入到佢私人電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5add23e817e7e296297721af88612a80054b49b0","tid":1002910,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"Chink thief"}]}